Sentencas: The purpose of the current study is to simulate the behavior of a solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) anode under sinusoidal excitation.
Titulo: Impedance simulation of a solid oxide fuel cell anode in time domain

Sentencas: The obtained harmonic response is used as a base for electrochemical impedance spectra simulation.
Titulo: Impedance simulation of a solid oxide fuel cell anode in time domain

Sentencas: The electrochemical impedance spectroscopy (EIS) is a powerful non-destructive tool for SOFC researches.
Titulo: Impedance simulation of a solid oxide fuel cell anode in time domain

Sentencas: In order to evaluate the EIS experimental results, efforts are devoted to develop EIS numerical simulation tools.
Titulo: Impedance simulation of a solid oxide fuel cell anode in time domain

Sentencas: In this study, a planar SOFC is modeled, and the steady state behavior and frequency response, as well as the electrochemical spectra of the anode, are obtained.
Titulo: Impedance simulation of a solid oxide fuel cell anode in time domain

Sentencas: The developed model couples the electrochemical kinetics with mass transport.
Titulo: Impedance simulation of a solid oxide fuel cell anode in time domain

Sentencas: The Butler-Volmer equation is used for the anode electrochemistry, and the species equations are used for gas transport in the anode channel.
Titulo: Impedance simulation of a solid oxide fuel cell anode in time domain

Sentencas: In order to solve the system of the nonlinear equations, an in-house code based on finite difference method is developed and utilized.
Titulo: Impedance simulation of a solid oxide fuel cell anode in time domain

Sentencas: A parametric study is also carried out, and the results are discussed.
Titulo: Impedance simulation of a solid oxide fuel cell anode in time domain

Sentencas: The simulation results are in good agreement with published data.
Titulo: Impedance simulation of a solid oxide fuel cell anode in time domain
